8. **HBV cure research (bepirovirsen + VIR-2218 + JNJ-3989) GalNAc siRNA + CRISPR cccDNA** = HBV functional cure → HCC 발생 risk 근본 감소. cross-hepatology + cross-gene_therapy_platform. quantum-VQE 의 RNA + DNA editing scaffold.
